5.2 Version 0.8.0 from 2026-12-16
=================================

   • Fix bugs related to automatic abbreviation expansion:
   • Backslash-dot-space now correctly expands to middledot-space, all
     while the cursor is positioned after the space character.
   • Adjacent abbreviations expand correctly, i.e.
     backslash-dot-backslash expands the first abbreviation, resulting
     in middledot-backslash.
   • Two abbreviations have been dropped, namely backslash and
     plus-space.


